    Descriptive, Reflexive
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MixedLinearisedSolver
    public abstract class MixedScheme
extends ImplicitScheme
    An abstraction describing a weighted semi-implicit finite-difference scheme for solving the one-dimensional heat conduction problem.
    See Also:
    ClassicalProblem, NonlinearProblem
